/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PP_GetValidationEngineManuallyMatchedPaymentReview                      
** Short Desc: Validation SP for Manually Matched Payment Review 
**                      
** Full Description: This procedure will validate whether manually matched payment is reviewed or not.        
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments: 
	 @UserID INT,
	 @Type Bit =1--auto 

**         
